data.description: This incredible tri level town home can be yours. But you’ll have to act fast. Special features like remote control blinds in the living room,  cable in every room, even the garage, and custom window coverings everywhere. A beautiful jacuzzi tub in the primary bath to soak your cares away. Huge rooms and an amazing gourmet kitchen. So many wonderful amenities, sparkling pool, cabana, and trails. All appliances convey, and all the furniture can be purchased except for the electronics. The security system with access innovations can be transferred at $28/mo. New HVAC in two upper floors June 2023. Great access to shopping, medical, and the freeway. If you’ve looked at all the wrong places then come see this one quick before it’s gone gone gone!
